2	 6,048		2.016
3	 9,072		3.024
4	12,096		4.032
5	15,120		5.040
6	18,144		6.048

At these speeds *dust* is a deadly hazard. And stray hydrogen atoms
hitting the hull may be a significant radiation hazard.

