> cf
> >- PESA, TL9, HP 16, PD 2, DR 2, 100 mi, 200 lbs, $ 800,000, 4 cf -
> >Radscanner, TL9, HP 40, PD 2, DR 2, 100 mi, 600 lbs, $ 550,000, 12 cf
> > Passive IR, Thermograph, Passive Radar, Scan Rating 23/29
> 
