>orbit).
>
>200 mi = ((accShip - accPlanet) x Time x Time) / 2
>
>200 mi = ((1.65g - 1g) x Time^2) / 2
>200 mi = ((0.65g) x Time^2) / 2
>
>(200 * 5280)ft = (((32 ft/(sec^2)) * 0.65)) / 2) ((x^2)(sec^2))
