    'date' => 'Thu, 21 Oct 99 00:03:28  0500',
    'body' => 'On 10/18/99 at 06:37 PM,  "Paul Campbell" <kemitixanzantix@freenet.co.uk> said:

>> Well, keep in mind that a few task systems that can be grafted on to GURPS
